### Wichtige Befehle

```bash
# ModSecurity Logs ansehen
tail -f {{ paths.nginx_log_dir[ansible_os_family] }}/modsec_audit.log

# nginx Error Log (ModSecurity Blocks)
tail -f {{ paths.nginx_log_dir[ansible_os_family] }}/error.log | grep -i modsec

# Regel temporaer deaktivieren (in nginx vHost):
# SecRuleRemoveById <REGEL-ID>

# ModSecurity Status pruefen
grep -i "modsecurity" {{ paths.nginx_conf[ansible_os_family] }}
```

